    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's risky but my doctor is always so dismissive about anything that isn't a prescription pill. i just feel like i'm being controlled by this stuff. if i was really careful and just did a massive amount of garlic extract and lots of greens every single day, wouldn't that eventually stabilize my levels naturally? like, it's just vitamins and herbs, how much danger could it really be compared to a harsh chemical like warfarin?",
